\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy governs the lifecycle of work order management within the Elko County Information Operations Department,
 from intake through authorized closure,
 and establishes the Deprecated Asset labor ceiling framework.
\end_layout

