\series default
 and shall accurately characterize the terminal outcome of the work.
 The available closure statuses and their definitions are established in work order operational standards maintained in the System of Engagement.
 The assigned technician shall document the five (5) business day notification requirement prior to closing work orders due to requester non-response,
 consistent with 
\series bold
Policy 
